title: Qatar Manufacturing Production
description: Manufacturing Production in Qatar increased 7.10 percent in August of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Manufacturing Production in Qatar averaged -0.45 percent from 2018 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 7.10 percent in August of 2022 and a record low of -8.73 percent in September of 2020. This page provides - Qatar Manufacturing Production- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Qatar Statistics Authority
